Priority: extra
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 10), cmake
Standards-Version: 3.9.8
Maintainer: Kunbus <admin@kunbus.de>
Homepage: https://revolution.kunbus.com/

Package: piserial
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ethtool
Description: Revolution Pi serial number utility
 Retrieve the RevPi's serial number from its Atmel CryptoAuth chip
 and generate the unique factory-default hostname and password.
 Revolution Pi is a set of IoT products based on the Raspberry Pi and
 geared towards industrial usage.
